## Context

Rocket mode currently only supports keyboard controls (WASD/QE). On mobile devices, the controls hint is hidden but there's no alternative input â€” the user can't actually fly. This adds a virtual joystick (left thumb, yaw+pitch) and a throttle button (right thumb, hold to accelerate) so mobile users can pilot through the star field.

